OL,3,CMan and woman deny murder of 'giggly
OL,4,Cand happy' toddler
OL,6,FA man and a woman have denied the
OL,7,Fmurder of a "giggly and happy" toddler.
OL,9,FTobias-John Doyle, who was 21 months
OL,10,Fold, died in hospital on 2 December,
OL,11,F2023. He had been taken there three
OL,12,Fdays earlier from a property on
OL,13,FMulberry Avenue in Leicester.
OL,15,FOmiel Gordon, 35, and Shalom Morgan,
OL,16,F23, were both charged with murder,
OL,17,Fcausing or allowing the death of a
OL,18,Fchild and cruelty to a person under
OL,19,Fthe age of 16.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
